      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems including patch tests, cantilever beam bending, and Hertzian contact were reproduced to within 1% of analytical solutions for all three FEA implementations in the ensemble."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
