      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study conducted with three refinement levels; Richardson extrapolation applied. Grid convergence index (GCI) for peak von Mises stress at screw-rod interface was below 2% for all ensemble members, confirming adequate spatial resolution."
