      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Independent analyst review performed for all three FEA implementations. Boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions were cross-checked against the ASTM F1717 protocol and documented in a formal model review record. No use errors identified."
    },
    {
