      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model is appropriate for titanium alloy components under quasi-static loading below yield. Frictional contact (mu=0.3) at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces is physically motivated and consistent with literature values for Ti-6Al-4V interfaces."
