      "rationale": "Material properties (E=114 GPa, nu=0.34 for Ti-6Al-4V) sourced from ASTM B265 certified material test reports for the specific lot used in the experimental constructs. Geometric dimensions measured from CMM data on three representative screws; variability less than 0.05 mm."
    },
    {
