      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single axial compressive load level (150 N) per ASTM F1717 protocol. The absence of multiple load conditions or load-displacement curve comparison across the full range of clinically relevant loads limits the achieved level to Gradation 2, below the required Gradation 3. This known gap is documented as an accepted residual uncertainty by the assessment team."
