      "rationale": "Validation activities directly replicate the ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol that constitutes the intended use scenario. The test configuration, loading mode, and construct geometry match the COU definition, providing high relevance. The ensemble approach across three independent FEA implementations strengthens confidence in the validation conclusion."
